Description: desktop timer app for the Pomodoro Technique
 A desktop timer app for the Pomodoro TechniqueÂ® written in C++ on top of Qt 5.
 .
 It's designed to be:
 .
   * Simple
   * Non-distracting
   * Unintrusive
   * Reasonably configurable
   * Extensible (with plugins)
   * Cross-platform
 When the application starts, a little tomato icon is shown on the system tray.
 Its color indicates the current state of the timer. By clicking on the tray
 icon the main application menu pops up.
